  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nI very like foundry,debug solidity is very great,but when i want to debug solidity behind a transaction,I didn't find a way to achieve.\r\n\r\nNow\r\n```\r\n forge test --match-path test/Cool.t.sol -vv --fork-url=XXX --fork-block-number 15223111\r\n```\r\nExpectation\r\n```\r\n forge test --match-path test/Cool.t.sol -vv --fork-url=XXX --fork-block-number 15223111  --tx-index 10\r\n```\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
